node.text:
I normally ride a 5’2 so this 5’10 stretched out retro fish outline for the Moonstone model which gives you unlimited speed and drive I class as a “sh-mid length” 

🎥 @shaggamang

node.title: Sh-Mid length surfing on a fresh @albumaustralia “Moonstone” model

node.text: The older I get, the more excited I get that It’s not just about the destination, it’s about loving the journey. Big thanks to @letsgomotorhomes for helping us enjoy the journey and @thredboresort for being such a epic destination!

Surf/Golf/Fine Food/Spa/Boating I’m beyond excited @wisemans to become a reality!
I only invest in things I believe in and will enjoy being a part of! I can’t wait to create memories with my family and friends in the mesmerizing landscape of Wisemans Ferry! 

Learn more @wisemans

Photo by Josh Kerr on July 23, 2021. May be an image of mountain, twilight, sky, tree, nature and lake.

Photo by Josh Kerr on July 23, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'This is Wisemans Surf Lodge: On-demand, perfect, A-frame waves, local, high-quality produce from a surf-side restaurant, space to lounge and recharge while the kids run wild. Six holes of golf, spas, cabanas and luxe rooms to stay the night just 60 minutes from the Sydney Harbour Bridge. Wisemans will be home to a new kind of surf community, chasing memories and sharing it with friends, new and old.'.
Photo by Josh Kerr on July 23, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text:
Some swells I’m not fussed and just need 1 or 2 to be frothing but this last one I felt like a bit of a pig and needed a feast 😂
Put 14 hours in the water in 2 days and had some mind boggling visions! Here’s a handful of filmed waves
Thanks Kirra ❤️
🎥 @shaggamang 

Riding- 5’10 “moonstone” W/Keel fins & 5’6 “Twinsman pintail” W/ powertwins
@albumsurf @albumaustralia

node.text:
🎉HAPPY 21ST BIRTHDAY 🎉
@colin_kerrazy 
I’m so proud to be your Dad and have loved watching you grow from a little Grom peeing on the road side on your 1st trip to Australia to you becoming the hard working loving man you are today! Thank you for being an amazing loving older brother to @sierrakerr and great son (at times) to your mum @nikki.kerr and I.
Enjoy your 1st Beer today 🤪
